  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK981">
<l>kaṭaṉeṉpa nallavai yellāṅ kaṭaṉaṟintu </l>
<l>cāṉṟāṇmai mēṟkoḷ pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is said that those who are conscious of their duty and behave with a perfect goodness will regard as natural all that is good.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
